name: Produkt Design
overview:
Produkt Design is a Industrial and Engineering Design Consultancy located in Melbourne, Australia. They focus on helping domestic and international manufacturers and engineering companies conquer their engineering challenges.

Founded in 2004, the company has rapidly grown gathering a team of talented individuals with expertise across a wide range of industries and crossing various disciplines.

Key business areas include Industrial and Mechanical Design, Finite Element Analysis, 2D to 3D Conversion, Project Management, Photorealistic Animation and Rendering, and SolidWorks consulting.

Their client list includes some of the most regarded Manufacturing and Engineering firms, across industries including Aerospace, Military, Automotive, Heavy Equipment, Food Processing, Consumer and Electronics.
